OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSlovak ministers agree to  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Freplace public broadcaster 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Slovak government has approved a   
OL,6, proposal to abolish the public         
OL,7, broadcaster and replace it with a new  
OL,8, body, prompting renewed fears for the  
OL,9, independence of the media under Robert 
OL,10, Fico's populist-nationalist coalition. 
OL,12,FThe cabinet backed a culture ministry  
OL,13,Fproposal to abolish the existing Radio 
OL,14,Fand Television of Slovakia (RTVS).     
OL,16,FIt will be replaced by a new body,     
OL,17,FSlovak Television and Radio (STVR).    
OL,19,FThe current director general, who was  
OL,20,Fappointed in 2022, will lose his job.  
